commentary: Mahmudullah to Rossouw, OUT Rossouw has been given out caught behind by umpire Gough as South Africa slip to 50 for 4. Rossouw and Miller converge and decide against a review. Looped up on off, grips in the pitch, keeps a bit low and spins away. Rossouw's balance is shot as he goes for a pull and nicks it behind via a bottom edge. Mushfiq swallows his third catch and Rossouw drags himself off the field..

Mushfiq swallows his third catch and Rossouw drags himself off the field..

commentary: Morkel to Soumya Sarkar, 2 runs Behardien misjudges it at sweeper cover. Tamim races down the track, Morkel drags his length back further and hurls it outside off. Carved over the covers, Behardien runs forward and across, dives to his left but does not even get a hand onto it as the ball drifts away from him. But that should have been taken, considering the modern standards
